{"tid":1614554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵你都幾撚柒串架喎","createTime":"2019-10-02T22:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T01:23:12.000Z","uid":96406,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"72cbe053255ece6706d4fa24775efc76282fdf05","tid":1614554,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T22:56:02.000Z","msg":"比人拆撚曬鐵 爆撚曬閘大大<br />\n夜晚就話可能部份車站明早未能開啟<br />\n點撚知第二朝就「所有車站如常服務」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好撚似話你知 <span style=\"color: red;\">係呀 你拆喇 第二朝我照太陽東邊升起 一樣安然無恙</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母喇黨鐵 係唔撚係就封鳩曬啲站 有不反對都照封 真係屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n封撚曬啲鐵攞黎運狗 你唔撚服務市民？<br />\n嫌比人拆唔夠？<br />\n831太子你封咁鳩耐？ CCTV你唔撚比？ <br />\n<br />\n我係呢度呼籲大家<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勿忘831</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n光復香港&middot;時代革命"},{"pid":"7fd536c1b9ccc9e331ca7a8de4bb35545ead89b1","tid":1614554,"uid":284304,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T22:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/By8hh_xIAAA2sql.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FBy8hh_xIAAA2sql.jpg%3Alarge&h=517553a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98595ee1cf537a2136bdd7c795fd6475d673d1ad","tid":1614554,"uid":289349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T22:58:17.000Z","msg":"英雄所見略同"},{"pid":"03aa2225f14abc8b875f0c950a0549affb125a53","tid":1614554,"uid":96406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:00:16.000Z","msg":"真係好撚柒串<br />\n與民為敵"},{"pid":"1e95f4cbae3b5406ff22114bbf19cb1707713f8e","tid":1614554,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:02:55.000Z","msg":"番工時間如常開放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.